tool_description: Sell on the Go. Accept credit cards and run your business on an iPhone, iPad, or Android device.  As a Square merchant, you can retrieve activity reports for your processed payments, refunds, and deposits with the Square Connect API. Pull these reports into your own custom-made applications to help you manage your business.

import requests

url = "https://community-square.p.rapidapi.com/me/payments"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "community-square.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
